      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴天石道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "巴天石",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘，这是烧饭瘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴天石微笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果见那青烟中夹有黑气，又有些白雾，乃是炊烟。众人都笑了起来，精神为之一振，都说：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钟灵给各人笑得不好意思，胀红了脸。王语嫣安慰她道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_dan_chen",
      "speaker_name": "朱丹臣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老婆婆，这里还有旁人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_dan_chen",
      "speaker_name": "朱丹臣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便只你一个在这里么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王语嫣笑着点头，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "巴天石",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们就都在这间屋中睡，别分散了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_dan_chen",
      "speaker_name": "朱丹臣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老婆婆可老得背了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是嗒嗒嗒、嗒嗒嗒的声音始终不停。巴天石跳了出去，抢过她的火刀火石来打，嗒嗒嗒几下，竟一点火星也无，摸上去也不是自己的打火之具，大声问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这句话一出口，随即哑然失笑：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴天石道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "两人即时收势",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘，是你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "巴天石",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来打火。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱丹臣道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "巴天石",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别追远了，保护公子要紧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "巴天石",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁有火刀火石？先点着了灯再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却是王语嫣和钟灵。巴天石和朱丹臣暗暗叫苦：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_dan_chen",
      "speaker_name": "朱丹臣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子，那老婆子曾向你借来用过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱丹臣道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钟灵突然尖声惊叫，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴天石心中一凛，说道：",
