      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的一声，捉住了木婉清的手臂。巴天石道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钟灵道：",
